Johnny English Strikes Again Review - A Weaker Spy Parody by Rowan Atkinson
It is already common to look for Brexit in every new film with a British tendency, which seems to be the case with this resurgence of Johnny English in a series of action parodies - which began in 2003 with Johnny English and was brought back to life in 2011 with Johnny English Reborn.
Will this sassy satire on how obviously a bad nation we are be our new export opportunity?
